ilul '''saint augustin''' (Aurelius Augustinus) s t Latinit di Tagast ass n 13 [[Tuber]] asegwas n 354, Iǧǧayaɣ ass n [[28 ɣuct]] asegwas n 430 di temdint n Hippone, yella d-amesnagay, d-amaru u d-amasnakuc, babas d yemmas d-imaziɣen, maca babas yuɣal d-amdan aṛumi, ma d yemmas teqqim d-tamdant tamaziɣt qqaṛen-as(sainte monique).

Yella d yiwen si kuz ivavaten n taknisa talatinit aked saint Amboise, saint Jérome et Grégoire Ier, daɣen d yiwen ger 33 n ṭebbat n taknisa. Yettwasmekta ass n 28 ɣuct n yal asegwas sɣur ikaṭulikiyen, ass n 15 yunyu sɣur urṭuduksiyen. Am umesnagay 


